description: Support to Hamutuk Harii Konfiansa (Support To The Trust-Building Pillar of The National Recovery Strategy)

subproject.corporate outcome: National and local institutions have the capacities to fulfill key functions of government for recovery in early post-crisis situations
subproject.description: The project supports the reconciliation and reintegration process of the National Recovery Strategy through managing a small grants fund for both national and international NGOs supporting trust-building activities at the community level and enhancing coordination among peace building actors in communities.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
subproject.title: Small grants fund for peace
